Versions of MyImg
-----------------

* Version 0.1 = 1st draft, too complex, later completely re-written 
* Version 0.2 = 2nd draft, better concept; functions: cut, crop, label, scalebar
* Version 0.3 = TODO: montage, scalebar/stripes, description, border...
